{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"16e9334bd8","title":"致中国民主同盟云南省委员会的公开信","origin":"《右派言行集(下集)》 (全校学生中部分右派言行)，中共云南大学委员会编，一九五七年九月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"60c2675dfe","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":16,"articleId":"16e9334bd8"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"120e6ca1c1","name":"蒋正富"},{"id":"684725707b","name":"昆明师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8d8d19c7ee","type":"title","text":"致中国民主同盟云南省委员会的公开信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"a5a596860f","type":"authors","text":"昆明师范学院蒋正富","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"6b9fb266cf","type":"paragraph","text":"〔中国民主同盟云南省委员会5月16日接到一封署名“师院学生启”的公开信。民盟省委把它转给了师院。公开信的全文如下）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"1bb5aaa9e7","type":"subtitle","text":"致民盟、民革、民建、致公党、农工党、九三学社——光明日报的公开信：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"124728e374","type":"subtitle","text":"喊贼作贼","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"32ff43d2c7","type":"paragraph","text":"昆明师院贴出所谓”反动标语’，这个秘密中的秘密，是共产党指使几个爪牙贴出，又指使中文系三年级逐条的反对，于是党支部就大吵大闹说：”有人在贴反动标语呀！我们警惕呀！发动大家看呀！……说明共产党言论自由呀！……’试问！这是解决矛盾吗？恐吓吗？欺骗吗？可耻！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"b147ac9c64","type":"subtitle","text":"“反动”言论没有，只有“正动”言论：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"29e31b195e","type":"paragraph","text":"㈠ 除一党专政，打倒卖国政府。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"56f74a6a43","type":"paragraph","text":"㈡ 废除丧权辱国的”中苏友好条约’，驱逐苏联专家(间谍)出境。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"9e3bbb0b66","type":"paragraph","text":"㈢ 要求民主党派执败，改善人民生活，维护人权，惩办卖国贼。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"402253ff7b","type":"paragraph","text":"㈣ 立即宣布师院开除的学生无效，解散党团特务组织，向(为)被迫害者的人复仇。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"7c8cf232e4","type":"paragraph","text":"㈤ 开放言论、信仰自由，打倒法西斯。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"},{"id":"c9bf387f8a","type":"paragraph","text":"㈥ 要求民主党派支持师院罢课，示威请愿。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8"}],"page":{"id":"ba54e009a9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"16e9334bd8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}